{"title":"数据结构代码实现：顺序表","uid":"f91e98bba144c54baafdbd5092ad4571","slug":"DataStructure-SequenceList","date":"2020-05-01T08:28:32.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:35.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-SequenceList.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200509170916.png","content":"<h2 id=\"顺序表的定义\"><a href=\"#顺序表的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顺序表的定义\"></a>顺序表的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">#define MaxSize 50\n#define ElemType int\n&#x2F;&#x2F;顺序表的定义\ntypedef struct &#123;\n    ElemType data[MaxSize];&#x2F;&#x2F;数据\n    int length;&#x2F;&#x2F;长度\n&#125;SqlList;</code></pre>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"顺序表的插入操作\"><a href=\"#顺序表的插入操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顺序表的插入操作\"></a>顺序表的插入操作</h2><ul>\n<li>判断插入的位置是否合法属于[1，l.length+1]</li>\n<li>判断储存空间是否已满</li>\n<li>将i位置后面的数据向后移动一位</li>\n<li>在i位置处插入数据</li>\n<li>长度加一<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200506173427.png\" alt=\"顺序表的插入操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 插入操作\n *&#x2F;\nbool ListInsert(SqlList &amp;l, int i, ElemType e) &#123;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;判断插入的位置是否合法属于[1，l.length+1]\n    if(i&lt;1||i&gt;l.length+1)&#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;判断储存空间是否已满\n    if(l.length&gt;&#x3D;MaxSize)&#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;将i位置后面的数据向后移动一位\n    for (int j&#x3D;l.length;j&gt;&#x3D;i;j--)&#123;\n        l.data[j]&#x3D;l.data[j-1];\n    &#125;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;在i位置处插入数据\n    l.data[i-1]&#x3D;e;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;长度加一\n    l.length++;\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"顺序表的删除操作\"><a href=\"#顺序表的删除操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顺序表的删除操作\"></a>顺序表的删除操作</h2></li>\n<li>判断删除的位置是否合法属于[1，l.length]</li>\n<li>获取要删除的数据</li>\n<li>把i位置后面的数据向前移一位</li>\n<li>长度减一<br><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200506173518.png\" alt=\"顺序表的删除操作\"><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 删除操作\n *&#x2F;\nbool ListDelete(SqlList &amp;l, int i, ElemType &amp;e) &#123;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;判断删除的位置是否合法属于[1，l.length]\n    if(i&lt;1||i&gt;l.length)&#123;\n        return false;\n    &#125;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;获取要删除的数据\n    e&#x3D;l.data[i-1];\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;把i位置后面的数据向前移一位\n    for(int j&#x3D;i;j&lt;l.length;j++)&#123;\n        l.data[j-1]&#x3D;l.data[j];\n    &#125;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;长度减一\n    l.length--;\n    return true;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"顺序表的查询操作\"><a href=\"#顺序表的查询操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顺序表的查询操作\"></a>顺序表的查询操作</h2></li>\n<li>循环查找元素值为e的数据，并返回其位序，否则返回0<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">&#x2F;*\n * 查询操作\n *&#x2F;\nint LocateElem(SqlList l, ElemType e) &#123;\n    int i;\n    &#x2F;&#x2F;循环查找元素值为e的数据，并返回其位序，否则返回0\n    for(i&#x3D;0;i&lt;l.length;i++)&#123;\n        if(l.data[i]&#x3D;&#x3D;e)&#123;\n            return i+1;\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n    return 0;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"顺序表的定义#define MaxSize 50 #define ElemType int &#x2F;&#x2F;顺序表的定义 typedef struct &#123; ElemType data[MaxSize];&#x2F;&#x2F;数据 int length;&#x2...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.6k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">顺序表的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A1%BA%E5%BA%8F%E8%A1%A8%E7%9A%84%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6